{"title":"Hexo更换主题(Themes)","uid":"221ff9b73c33c8c7328587ca0c7f4edc","slug":"hexo/003-hexo-themes","date":"2022-01-21T07:38:47.000Z","updated":"2022-01-22T17:24:36.882Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo/003-hexo-themes.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://t7.baidu.com/it/u=2179558408,1225199077&fm=193&f=GIF","content":"<hr>\n<p>默认主题是比较丑的，如果有必要，可以尝试<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\">官网主题</a>进行更换。</p>\n<h3 id=\"clone主题\"><a href=\"#clone主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"clone主题\"></a>clone主题</h3><p>找到喜欢的主题，先clone仓库代码，</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/chunqiuyiyu/hexo-theme-polk themes/polk<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>执行完成后，会发现themes文件夹多了一个polk的主题文件夹。</p>\n<h3 id=\"配置主题\"><a href=\"#配置主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置主题\"></a>配置主题</h3><p>打开_config.yml文件，修改theme的配置</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-conf\" data-language=\"conf\"><code class=\"language-conf\">theme: polk<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"发布主题\"><a href=\"#发布主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"发布主题\"></a>发布主题</h3><p>因为修改了配置文件，则需要clean掉静态资源文件，进行重新生成；此处只演示本地，如果需要发布到远端，将s改成d即可。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo cl <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> hexo s -g<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n","text":" 默认主题是比较丑的，如果有必要，可以尝试官网主题进行更换。 clone主题找到喜欢的主题，先clone仓库代码， git clone https://github.com/chunqiuyiyu/hexo-theme-polk themes/polk 执行完成后，会发现them...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":293,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":6,"path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"},{"name":"Themes","slug":"Hexo/Themes","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Hexo/Themes.json"}],"